posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 28', 'OR Text', '28', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 912 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'OPENING OCTOBER 2022!', 'The Ruby Creek neighborhood of Port Orchard welcomes you home to Haven, where modern conveniences meet nature’s bounty.', 'Discover a new sanctuary with Haven’s garden-style apartments—walkable to most anything and a respite from nearly everything.', 'Features:', 'Spacious walk-in closets*, Balcony or patio for every unit, Lush park-like views, Luxury vinyl flooring, Washer and dryer in every unit, Kitchen Islands*, Quartz counters with high-end finishes, Stainless steel appliances, Primary suites', '*Only available in select apartments', 'Community Amenities:', "Fitness center, Controlled access, BBQs, Outdoor lounge, Gated entry, Dog park, Large summer lawn, Clubhouse with caterer's kitchen, Bus stop, Firepits, Play areas, Heated resort-style pool, Grills, Parcel pending package lockers, Covered outdoor spa, Integrated trails, Picnic shelter with grill, Smoke Free, Playground, Billiards, ping pong, and shuffleboard, Lawn games, Picnic shelters, Theatre-inspired media room, Business center/Coworking space", 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Policy Type: Cat, Dog', 'Max Number of Pets: 2', 'Pet deposit fee min/max: $300 - $450', 'Pet monthly rent min/max: $25 - $50', 'Pet policy fee min/max: $200 - $400', 'Income Requirements:', 'Three Times Rent', 'Want more info on this unit?', 'See the link (below):', '<URL>', 'Port Orchard Apartments Kitsap Apartments Bremerton Apartments', 'OKZ1q9iG']
